  "detailed_description": "Dive into a strange and mesmerizing world where gravity is unpredictable and the laws of physics are constantly defied.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Out of this world</h2><br>Matter is a first-person parkour game that will plunge you into an unknown and mysterious dimension. You will need to use your agility and wits to overcome obstacles and discover the secrets of a strange reality.<br><br>The action takes place in a world that is both fascinating and strange. You will need to explore this universe in search of answers, but be careful not to get lost in its twists and turns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Altered senses</h2><br>Gravity is a central element of Matter. It is unpredictable and can change at any moment. You will need to adapt to these changes to avoid falling into the void...<br><br>Matter is an intense and fast-paced action-adventure game. You will need to overcome increasingly difficult obstacles to progress. The adventure is interspersed with short puzzles that will require you to use several of your senses. Don't worry, the journey remains very accessible, anyone can make it through.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A thrilling 30-minute adventure</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A platform game with a pleasant and serene atmosphere</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Disorienting and exotic landscapes</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A relaxing, dynamic, and disorienting soundtrack</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- No violence</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- No competition</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Just fun!</ul><br>Important note: Please be advised that due to camera rotations and constantly altered perception, details may appear rapidly on screen and your sense of balance may be severely disrupted. For anyone who has ever experienced photosensitive epilepsy or motion sickness, it is not recommended to purchase or play this game as the risk of causing these episodes is real.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/c6e129312df85425f72507261fb12407.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/c6e129312df85425f72507261fb12407.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/c6e129312df85425f72507261fb12407.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits</h2><br>Game Design, Programming & Publishing by<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>@MatoLabu</strong></ul><br>Music, Sound & Tech Art by<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>@Tomavatars</strong> member of Concrete Games</ul><br>2D & 3D Graphics by<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Monf</strong></ul><br>Game Design, Level Building, VFX & Programming by<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Paul Vaillé</strong></ul><br>Publishing & Community Management by<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Le Mauvais Joueur</strong></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4c60bf8dd28966bd1446bca5b3efd728.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4c60bf8dd28966bd1446bca5b3efd728.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4c60bf8dd28966bd1446bca5b3efd728.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Dive into a strange and mesmerizing world where gravity is unpredictable and the laws of physics are constantly defied.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/16c5f9bd2b6002469d5cb899875f800b.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Out of this world</h2><br>Matter is a first-person parkour game that will plunge you into an unknown and mysterious dimension. You will need to use your agility and wits to overcome obstacles and discover the secrets of a strange reality.<br><br>The action takes place in a world that is both fascinating and strange. You will need to explore this universe in search of answers, but be careful not to get lost in its twists and turns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/e1a64fbba7e8977d340939ac4c8fbe73.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Altered senses</h2><br>Gravity is a central element of Matter. It is unpredictable and can change at any moment. You will need to adapt to these changes to avoid falling into the void...<br><br>Matter is an intense and fast-paced action-adventure game. You will need to overcome increasingly difficult obstacles to progress. The adventure is interspersed with short puzzles that will require you to use several of your senses. Don't worry, the journey remains very accessible, anyone can make it through.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.poster.avif?t=1729692337\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.webm?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/4fe3ed54cc7c40e9355a0332a6738510.mp4?t=1729692337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A thrilling 30-minute adventure</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A platform game with a pleasant and serene atmosphere</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Disorienting and exotic landscapes</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- A relaxing, dynamic, and disorienting soundtrack</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- No violence</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- No competition</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">- Just fun!</ul><br>Important note: Please be advised that due to camera rotations and constantly altered perception, details may appear rapidly on screen and your sense of balance may be severely disrupted. For anyone who has ever experienced photosensitive epilepsy or motion sickness, it is not recommended to purchase or play this game as the risk of causing these episodes is real.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978250/extras/c6e129312df85425f72507261fb